{"about_the_game":"In Konkwest your world domination campaign takes a single session. Take control of a country, and shape its history turn by turn. Plan its developments, its conquests, and its defenses. Make your plans simultaneously with all other countries and see them change the world.<br><br><strong>Simultaneous Turns around the World</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Get rid of your flat map game, and accept the curve in Konkwest's globe view<br></li><li> Reject sequentialism, embrace simultaneous planning, don\u2019t wait endlessly for your turn</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702570/extras/steam_description_button_scenarios.png?t=1723980639\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2024 - Play (almost) any state in our modern world, even unrecognized ones<br></li><li> 2000 - That's over 20 years ago already, isn't that crazy?<br></li><li> 1900 - The buildup to WW1 belongs in any historical strategy map game<br></li><li> 1700 - Big Poland, big Sweden, big Ottoman Empire, what\u2019s not to love<br></li><li> 1300 - Experience the Holy Roman Empire at its height in a Medieval World<br></li><li> 0 (1BC) - Challenge the great ancient empires of Rome and China, or lead them to world domination<br></li><li> Balanced - A custom scenario where the world is divided up between equally sized countries<br></li><li> Kaiserzeit 1926 - A unique alternate history created for an unknown board game</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702570/extras/steam_description_button_countries.png?t=1723980639\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Create your own country in any place, and give it a unique identity<br></li><li> Change its name, its color, and its policies to your liking<br></li><li> Add other countries to your world, and see them expand or fail</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702570/extras/steam_description_button_multiplayer.png?t=1723980639\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play with many other players in a single session <br></li><li> Connect with friends and others through the game's community</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723980639","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702570/page.bg.jpg?t=1723980639","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723980639","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702570/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723980639","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Konkwest includes abstract displays of violence through iconography and firework effects. Due to the game's setting it inherently involves political and historical topics."},"demos":[{"appid":2977450,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"In Konkwest your world domination campaign takes a single session. Take control of a country, and shape its history turn by turn. Plan its developments, its conquests, and its defenses. Make your plans simultaneously with all other countries and see them change the world.<br><br><strong>Simultaneous Turns around the World</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Get rid of your flat map game, and accept the curve in Konkwest's globe view<br></li><li> Reject sequentialism, embrace simultaneous planning, don\u2019t wait endlessly for your turn</li></ul><br><img clas